          },
          "blocks": {
            "accordion_row_9xiUkL": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What types of ingredients are used in the Cala Falcó Collection?",
                "open_by_default": true,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 200
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_NcagX7": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>The Cala Falcó Collection is crafted using premium natural ingredients, such as essential oils, botanical extracts, and Mediterranean herbs. You’ll find ingredients like lavender, rosemary, almond oil, and citrus fruits, all selected for their mood-enhancing and skin-nourishing properties​.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_NcagX7"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_dGrwcq": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "How does the Cala Falcó Collection incorporate mood programming into its products?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_iJXFbN": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Our collections are designed to influence emotions and mental states through aromachology. By using ingredients known for their calming, energizing, or balancing effects, such as lavender, bergamot, and mint, our perfumes, diffusers, and candles help you create an atmosphere that suits your mood.​</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_iJXFbN"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_hMWV3V": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What makes the Cala Falcó Collection sustainable?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_T7K3WL": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>We focus on sustainable sourcing for our natural ingredients, ensuring that our products are both luxurious and environmentally conscious. Our eco-friendly packaging and commitment to biodegradable surfactants reflect our dedication to minimising environmental impact​.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_T7K3WL"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_GP8mBP": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Are the Cala Falcó Collection  handcrafted?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_kEGHRY": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yes, each product is meticulously handcrafted in small batches. This artisanal approach ensures that every fragrance, cosmetic, and diffuser is made with care and precision, resulting in a unique, high-quality experience​.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
